<span id="freeTextContainer5444209423589792813">There are too many things this American writer does not know about Victorian England. The book does not ring true. It is his first; perhaps he will improve. I hope so, because I do like the idea of an aristocratic amateur sleuth who reads Trollope and Shakespeare while sipping his tea. Oh wait—isn&apos;t that Lord Peter?</span>
